    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>17 June 1862</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Revd Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Being informed by<lb/>
                <persName>Mr Joel</persName> that he has relen-<lb/>quished your agency, I shall
                be<lb/> glad to undertake the same<lb/> and suppose under similar<lb/> arrangements,
                should you<lb/> be willing so to do. An early<lb/> intimation will oblige as I<lb/>
                should then advertise. I suppose<lb/> my name is known to you<lb/> not only as a
                Bookseller<lb/> &amp; Publisher of nine years<lb/> standing but also as
                Secretary<lb/> to most of the Jewish Institu<lb/>tions in
                    <placeName>London</placeName></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Yours Truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <persName role="author">S Solomon</persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>PS. Should you desire<lb/> any reference, I can<lb/> furnish you with<lb/>
                satisfactorily</p>
        </body>
    </text>
